name: podamShouldBeAbleToManufactureAnyTypeOfMaps

testSteps.description: When I invoke the factory manufacturing for class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.UnsupportedMapInConstructorPojo with specific types {class java.lang.String,class java.lang.Integer}
Then the pojo uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.UnsupportedMapInConstructorPojo@5aec2c must be of the type class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.UnsupportedMapInConstructorPojo
Then the Map should not be null or empty and each element should have key of type class java.lang.String and value of type class java.lang.Integer

title: Podam should be able to manufacture any type of Maps
